additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Wheat Flour (Thiamine), Dried Mixed Fruit (24%) (Sultanas, Currants, Glace Citrus Peel (Orange Peel, Glucose, Sugar, Citric Acid)), Water, Sugar, Margarine (Vegetable Oils, Water, Salt, Milk Solids, Emulsifiers (471, 472c), Antioxidant (304, 307), Natural Flavour, Natural Colour (Carotene)), Thickener (1412), Dextrose, Whey Powder (Milk), Lemon Juice Concentrate, Salt, Natural Flavours, Cinnamon, Raising Agent (Sodium Bicarbonate), Processing Aid (Wheat), Citric Acid.

description: With a deep pie crust, delicately spiced fruit mince filling and delicious golden crumble, this dessert is a guaranteed crowd pleaser! Ready to share with friends, family or unexpected guests, perfect for special celebrations!
name: Fruit Mince Crumble Pie
